quote><br />\n<br />\n唔係得12集嗎？<br />\n<br />\n應該睇曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為你睇之前有期待，所以冇想像中咁好睇<br />\n而我地睇之前當晒子供向咁睇，所以喜出望外"},{"pid":"ef8a887162f602dd3ae88ed28e8048c490b7e3d3","tid":218233,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">魔法戰爭？</span></span>"},{"pid":"14ebf240029345b355e9299a4447082ef0ad297f","tid":218233,"uid":90562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1514521625288166&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=444209758986030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1514521625288166%26substory_index%3D0%26id%3D444209758986030&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0wdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4756f521\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1514521625288166&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=444209758986030</a><br />\n好文共享<br />\n利申唔識欣賞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得幾好起碼等我知道佢欣賞啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過空氣系真係好虛無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfb73b011428808074c5ec4643fd3c796b3ed04","tid":218233,"uid":90562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你睇哂未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係得12集嗎？<br />\n<br />\n應該睇曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為你睇之前有期待，所以冇想像中咁好睇<br />\n而我地睇之前當晒子供向咁睇，所以喜出望外</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係如果你地唔講，冇期待，我睇完第一第二集應該放棄！"},{"pid":"42270df46dbb4c54b0ceb126cba223cc0224e63c","tid":218233,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>(非罵戰)之前連登有班話好睇，我睇咗之後唔覺得有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇下你地用咩觀賞嘅方法，我係咪用錯咗方法睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好睇夾唔夾電波，我睇個陣第一二集已經覺得幾好睇<br />\n我鐘意佢一開始有曬大綱，每集一個新地域，新人物，穩定發展，好有旅遊feel，睇得好舒服<br />\n旅遊得黎又會含蓄地埋下伏線同線索，比到你驚喜"},{"pid":"4bc5726b4b43061dc3f50f9a748498d1589010c0","tid":218233,"uid":90562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你睇哂未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係得12集嗎？<br />\n<br />\n應該睇曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為你睇之前有期待，所以冇想像中咁好睇<br />\n而我地睇之前當晒子供向咁睇，所以喜出望外</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係如果你地唔講，冇期待，我睇完第一第二集應該放棄！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來子供向=兒童閱讀，而家都算係子供向，冇黑化冇複雜設定，小朋友一定睇得明，不過小朋友唔知會唔會覺得悶，而家好多小朋友作品都複雜過佢！"},{"pid":"d8b68dab418c11ebb1a4822a40c80f34e4975258","tid":218233,"uid":90562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>(非罵戰)之前連登有班話好睇，我睇咗之後唔覺得有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇下你地用咩觀賞嘅方法，我係咪用錯咗方法睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好睇夾唔夾電波，我睇個陣第一二集已經覺得幾好睇<br />\n我鐘意佢一開始有曬大綱，每集一個新地域，新人物，穩定發展，好有旅遊feel，睇得好舒服<br />\n旅遊得黎又會含蓄地埋下伏線同線索，比到你驚喜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇佢D人解說動物，先至覺得有D興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d65285aa9f7b6b54abd3781ad7cf63556b985db","tid":218233,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>(非罵戰)之前連登有班話好睇，我睇咗之後唔覺得有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇下你地用咩觀賞嘅方法，我係咪用錯咗方法睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好睇夾唔夾電波，我睇個陣第一二集已經覺得幾好睇<br />\n我鐘意佢一開始有曬大綱，每集一個新地域，新人物，穩定發展，好有旅遊feel，睇得好舒服<br />\n旅遊得黎又會含蓄地埋下伏線同線索，比到你驚喜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇佢D人解說動物，先至覺得有D興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇國家地理頻道"},{"pid":"f45363c1043e45fc726793833